RACE.FOOTNOTES: WILL KNOWS pressed wide early, challenged four-wide turn, dueled outside into stretch, crowded rival through stretch, prevailed late. SPEEDY FELLAR dueled three-wide to late turn, dueled inside into stretch, was crowded for the entire drive, gave way late. TOWARDS THE LIGHT dueled inside early, forced pace into turn, gave way mid turn. OHTANI dueled between horses from the two-path early, dropped back early turn, faded. The rider aboard SPEEDY FELLAR lodged a claim of foul against the rider of WILL KNOWS for interference through the stretch. As a result, WILL KNOWS was disqualified and placed second.
